            Federal Interagency Forum on Aging-Related Statistics

                      Freedom of Information Act Notice
    _____________________________________________________________________

   Welcome to the Forum FOIA Home Page. We hope you will find this site
   informative and that it will facilitate your efforts to obtain public
   information about the programs of the member agencies of the Forum.
   Since the forum is an interagency committee and not an agency, its
   activities are covered under the FOIA activities of its member
   agencies.

   Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) as amended by Public Law 104-231 (HHS
   Web Site)

   HHS FOIA Page (covers the Office of the Assistant Secretary for
   Planning and Evaluation)

   Centers for Disease Control FOIA Page (covers the National Center for
   Health Statistics)

   Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services (formerly HCFA) FOIA Page

   National Institutes of Health FOIA Page (covers the National Institute
   on Aging)

   Administration on Aging FOIA Page

   Social Security Administration FOIA Page

   Bureau of Labor Statistics FOIA Page

   Department of Commerce FOIA Page (covers the Census Bureau)
